AVAILABILITY OF THESE LICENSES MAY ENABLE COMPETITORS TO DEVELOP SOFTWARE PRODUCTS THAT BETTER MIMIC THE FUNCTIONALITY OF MICROSOFTS OWN PRODUCTS WHICH COULD

