2006 WILL FOCUS ON DEVELOPMENT OF WINDOWS VISTA, THE NEXT-GENERATION PC OPERATING SYSTEM, AND WILL INCLUDE MARKETING INITIATIVES SUCH AS THE GLOBAL START SOMETHING CAMPAIGN.

